body:
*This is a response to the anonymous Tony/Pepper question I got in my ask box* (I can’t publish it because of the spoiler in your question) 

*endgame/pepperony spoilers below*

Q: Can you tell me if Tony and Pepper kiss (other than the kiss on the cheek when he dies) or have any sweet moments together?

Hello… Umm, I can’t really remember if there is a kiss, If there was it wasn’t a big special moment but yes there are some really nice scenes! Especially at the beginning of the movie during the 5 year time gap space… It’s just really cute and I wish we could have a whole movie about that little period of time!
